metadata.name: Gotham in Istanbul
metadata.description:
Gotham in Istanbul
The city that Batman is protecting is called Gotham. 
It is often known as dirty, with a high crime rate.
Is always dark. Every city has a Gotham side, but it doesn't have a hero. Every time I look from Üsküdar to Beşiktaş, I think of Gotham.

Dimension : 4462*6135
Date : 26/12/2008
300dpi 24 bit
